query:
DELETE FROM storage_logs USING (
                    SELECT
                        *
                    FROM
                        storage_logs
                    WHERE
                        miniblock_number BETWEEN $1 AND $2
                ) AS batches_to_prune
                WHERE
                    storage_logs.miniblock_number < $1
                    AND batches_to_prune.hashed_key = storage_logs.hashed_key
